#Repost • @lakmefashionwk || @lakmesalon X @chola_the_label's presents 'The Awakening' at FDCI x Lakme Fashion Week. The collection artistically brings out the concept of letting go, being relaxed and experiencing the small pleasures of life onto a canvas of fluid clothes. 

Foraying into the nature of fluidity, the line features a burst of colours while maintaining the brand's signature black and white palette. 

@lakmeindia @fdciofficial @r1seworldwide
